SCOPE OF THIS LICENSE

This MIT License applies to the following components of CodeRisk:

✅ INCLUDED (Open Source):
- CLI tool (crisk binary and source code in cmd/crisk/)
- Local mode infrastructure (docker-compose.yml)
- Core graph engine (internal/graph/, internal/ingestion/)
- Phase 1 baseline metrics (internal/metrics/)
- Pre-commit hook system (internal/hooks/)
- Tree-sitter parsing (internal/treesitter/)
- Local database schemas and migrations

❌ NOT INCLUDED (Proprietary):
- Cloud infrastructure and multi-tenant platform
- ARC (Architectural Risk Catalog) database contents
- Phase 2 LLM investigation algorithms
- Cross-organization pattern learning system
- AI code provenance and trust certificates
- Insurance underwriting algorithms
- Enterprise features (SSO, audit logs, self-hosted)
- Commercial cloud services and APIs

COMMERCIAL CLOUD PLATFORM:
The CodeRisk cloud platform, including multi-tenant infrastructure, the ARC
database, trust infrastructure, and enterprise features, is proprietary and
available under separate commercial license terms. See https://coderisk.dev
for cloud platform pricing and licensing.

